                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/857.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Vice Consul at Puerto
                            Plata</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Puerto Plata</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-09-04T15:00:00-04:40">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 4, 1913—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Governor Céspedes on Tuesday issued a manifesto here declaring the province
                    severed from the central Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Esteva</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
